data.meta_description: John Helfrich Dies After Brief Illness   John F. Helfrich, 71, died at 5:30 Sunday evening at St Elizabeth. Ill two weeks, he had entered the hospital Tuesday of last week.   Mr Helfrich was born in Pulaski county Sept 16, 1887, the son of George B and Sarah J. Zeller Helfrich, and had spent all of his life in the...
